<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lungngaihna lummei kalah,
 Nga bang ka leng ie;
 Kipahna ni eng a tuoi,
 Taikhuo val theilo.

[V2]
 Aw nunnawpna ni, mu bang ka ngai,
 Ka chungah hung vakin;
 Thimna dogal lienin ei nang ie,
 Aw, hung vakin, Na kumsawt gam;
 Nawpna pielgal ah thuong ei tunin.

[V3]
 2. Adam than thimsung ahin,
 Aw Na eng ngaiin;
 Tatna thisan lun zalin,
 Nang ka hun sam hi.

[V4]
 3. Khawvel mauna'n a dim hi,
 Nam tin chitin di'n;
 Aw Eden ni eng tuoi nung,
 Mu bang ka ngai ie,

[V5]
 4. Lautha khawvel ninnuom ah,
 Laituol I len tieng;
 Thim lal galhat nuoi zinmang,
 Chu nuoisieh tai tiu.</lyrics>
<title>Kipahna ni eng</title>
<author>Kamlala</author>
<hymn_number>114</hymn_number>
</song>